    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/84b264d820093666821af85c46671ee2.avif?t=1770340890\" width=616 height=376 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/2d23578478f26b644f33a4beb9f0462f.webp?t=1770340890\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半龙半人的公主，艾法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >艾法的执事，普菲尔。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两人所到之处，是栖息着众多魔物娘的不可思议孤岛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普菲尔为了满足艾法深不见底的食量，开始在岛上收集食物，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然而这座岛屿，似乎在表面之下隐藏着某个秘密ーーー。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/f9b084fef737ed9147e0e53ac18d176b.webp?t=1770340890\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作是以探索为主的ARPG游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(1)探索地图，打倒怪物，为艾法收集食物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(2)从艾法处获得褒奖，提升技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(3)打倒栖息于地图中的BOSS，获得高级食材。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180550/extras/930eb57c84213306e6d1f045f093d9b7.webp?t=1770340890\" width=616 height=55 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动画CG</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可强化技能</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可选择10种特效各异的武器</p></li></ul>",
